WarmUp-1 : diff21

Given an int n, return the absolute difference between n and 21, except return double the absolute difference if n is over 21.

public int diff21(int n) {
// setting our target variable to 21
  int targetNumber = 21;
        if(n >= 21) {
      //checking if m is greater than or equal to 21
      //if so, we use the Math class to calculate the absloute number of n - targetNumber * 2
            return Math.abs(n - targetNumber) * 2;
        } else {
      //if not, we use the Math class to calculate the absolute number of n - targetNumber
            return Math.abs(n - targetNumber);
        }
    }

